when you write a paper or write a thesis-
或是写论文时

36
00:02:32,610 --> 00:02:34,410
some of you are thesis writers,
你们当中有人在写论文

37
00:02:34,950 --> 00:02:38,020
what you do is very often mix them.
你们常犯的错误是将它们混淆了

38
00:02:38,270 --> 00:02:40,680
So you have preparation.Then you write a little bit.
通常你们会先准备 然后写一些

39
00:02:40,930 --> 00:02:42,690
And then you take a break.You have an insight.
之后休息一下 会有一些顿悟

40
00:02:42,890 --> 00:02:45,440
Then you go back to more preparation and on and on.
再开始作更多准备等等

41
00:02:45,670 --> 00:02:50,570
This is just a general outline,which is useful in a few ways.
这只是一个轮廓 某些角度来看是很有用的

42
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,250
First of all,
首先

43
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:55,910
it is useful in that we can understand by looking at it.
我们光看着它就能明白

44
00:02:56,130 --> 00:02:57,410
There's no quick fix.
没有捷径

45
00:02:57,660 --> 00:03:02,650
None of the great creative artists,scientists,
历史上所有的艺术家 科学家

46
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:07,710
business people in history,created in a vacuum.
商界名人都不是凭空出世的

47
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:11,010
Initially they became experts in their fields.
他们首先得成为各自领域的专家

48
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:14,250
