00:16:02,490 --> 00:16:05,460
What she did specifically was taking the instructions
她的做法明确地根据

270
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:09,190
from Abraham Maslow's work on peak experience.
Abraham Maslow关于巅峰经验的研究

271
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:11,050
And here are the instructions.
以下就是做法

272
00:16:11,290 --> 00:16:13,810
Once again,this was three times,15 minutes,
三次 15分钟

273
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:16,480
so 45 minutes total on three consecutive days.
连续三天 总共45分钟

274
00:16:17,290 --> 00:16:18,910
"Think of the most wonderful experience
"想出生命中最精彩的经历…

275
00:16:19,130 --> 00:16:23,160
or experiences in your life,happiest moments,ecstatic moments,
或多次美好的经历 快乐 兴奋的时刻

276
00:16:23,430 --> 00:16:26,300
moments of rapture,perhaps from being in love,
或坠入爱河极度欢喜的时刻

277
00:16:26,580 --> 00:16:29,670
or from listening to music,or suddenly ‘being hit’
或者听音乐时的欢快时刻 或突然…

278
00:16:29,940 --> 00:16:33,380
by a book or painting or from some great creative moment.
发现一本好书或好画或突然灵感乍现"

