00:23:34,330 --> 00:23:36,200
we need to focus on the origins of health.
我们要关注的是健康的始源

408
00:23:36,430 --> 00:23:39,140
Saluto- health; genesis- origin.
Saluto是健康 genesis是本源

409
00:23:41,230 --> 00:23:43,710
And what he did specifically was the following.
他的具体做法如下

