00:24:42,040 --> 00:24:43,690
And he said we need to study those.
他说我们要研究这些人

428
00:24:43,940 --> 00:24:46,150
We shouldn't just study the sick people,
不该只研究有病的人

429
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:52,360
whether the sick people who are physically ill-
不管是身体健康有问题的病人

